# prefix-block-tab-indent-inner

## Input

```
s. {
	a 1
  b 2
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..18
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..18
    WORD_KEY@0..2
      WORD@0..2 "s."
    SPACE@2..3 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@3..4 "{"
    NEWLINE@4..5 "\n"
    ERROR@5..9
      TAB@5..6 "\t"
      WORD@6..7 "a"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      NUMERAL@8..9 "1"
    NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
    SPACE@10..12 "  "
    ENTRY@12..16
      WORD_KEY@12..13
        WORD@12..13 "b"
      SPACE@13..14 " "
      INTEGER@14..15
        NUMERAL@14..15 "2"
      NEWLINE@15..16 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@16..17 "}"
    NEWLINE@17..18 "\n"
```

## Syntax Error

```
[
    SyntaxError {
        message: "tab indent is not allowed, skipping this line",
        range: 5..5,
    },
]
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..2 "s.",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@3..4 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@12..13 "b",
                    },
                    value: Integer {
                        sign: none,
                        numeral: NUMERAL@14..15 "2",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@16..17 "}",
        },
    ],
}
```

